text: Jakkanna is a 2016 Telugu film directed by Vamsi Krishna Akella. The film features Sunil and Mannara Chopra in the lead roles, with Kabir Duhan Singh and Saptagiri playing supporting roles. Jakkanna released on 29 July 2016. Later Hindi Dubbed Version Right Sold Tollywood Films and received industry hit talk from critics Studio (Arvind Patel) == Plot == A man's (Sunil) attempts to repay a kindness earns him the wrath of a ruthless gangster. == Cast == * Sunil as Ganesh alias Jakkanna * Mannara Chopra as Sahasra * Kabir Duhan Singh as Bairagi * Prudhvi as Katakatala Kattappa * Saptagiri as Kung Fu Instructor == Soundtrack == {| class="wikitable" |- !
